snippet: Three playoff spots, most of the playoff seeds and the top pick in next year’s draft are still up for grabs as the league winds down to its final weekend.
abstract: Analysis notes that three playoff spots, most of the playoff seeds and the top pick in next year’s draft are still up for grabs as the NFL winds down to its final weekend; assesses playoff picture and which coaches may loose their jobs.
